HEADWORD: Federation
<hw>Fed`er*a"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>f⟦eacute⟧d⟦eacute⟧ration</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of
